He has produced two independently released albums, Retrieval Structure (2011) and Perception (2013).
He is the inaugural winner of the APRA Art Music Award for Excellence In Jazz in 2012.
He received the Helpmann Academy's Keith Michell Award in 2010, The first time a jazz musician had ever won the award.
He has also won Downbeat Jazz Awards for 'Jazz Soloist' in 2012 and 2014  and 'Jazz Composition' in 2011, 2012 and 2014.
